me.matt.luka.interfaces

Interface Map<K,V>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Dictionary

    public interface Map<K,V>
    Interface for a class of type map which stores key-value associations. Note: for the Luka Virtual Machine project, a map can contain duplicate keys.
